CreateOperations.Name: CreateOrUpdate
CreateOperations.Description: Creates or updates a move collection.

ListOperations.Name: GetAll
ListOperations.Description: Get all the Move Collections in the resource group.

OperationsFromSubscriptionExtension.Name: GetMoverResourceSets
OperationsFromSubscriptionExtension.Description: Get all the Move Collections in the subscription.

OtherOperations.Name: Prepare
OtherOperations.Description: Initiates prepare for the set of resources included in the request body. The prepare operation is on the moveResources that are in the moveState 'PreparePending' or 'PrepareFailed', on a successful completion the moveResource moveState do a transition to MovePending. To aid the user to prerequisite the operation the client can call operation with validateOnly property set to true.

OtherOperations.Name: InitiateMove
OtherOperations.Description: Moves the set of resources included in the request body. The move operation is triggered after the moveResources are in the moveState 'MovePending' or 'MoveFailed', on a successful completion the moveResource moveState do a transition to CommitPending. To aid the user to prerequisite the operation the client can call operation with validateOnly property set to true.

OtherOperations.Name: Commit
OtherOperations.Description: Commits the set of resources included in the request body. The commit operation is triggered on the moveResources in the moveState 'CommitPending' or 'CommitFailed', on a successful completion the moveResource moveState do a transition to Committed. To aid the user to prerequisite the operation the client can call operation with validateOnly property set to true.

OtherOperations.Name: Discard
OtherOperations.Description: Discards the set of resources included in the request body. The discard operation is triggered on the moveResources in the moveState 'CommitPending' or 'DiscardFailed', on a successful completion the moveResource moveState do a transition to MovePending. To aid the user to prerequisite the operation the client can call operation with validateOnly property set to true.

OtherOperations.Name: ResolveDependencies
OtherOperations.Description: Computes, resolves and validate the dependencies of the moveResources in the move collection.

OtherOperations.Name: BulkRemove
OtherOperations.Description: Removes the set of move resources included in the request body from move collection. The orchestration is done by service. To aid the user to prerequisite the operation the client can call operation with validateOnly property set to true.

OtherOperations.Name: GetRequiredForResources
OtherOperations.Description: List of the move resources for which an arm resource is required for.

OtherOperations.Name: GetUnresolvedDependencies
OtherOperations.Description: Gets a list of unresolved dependencies.

CreateOperations.Name: CreateOrUpdate
CreateOperations.Description: Creates or updates a Move Resource in the move collection.

UpdateOperations.Name: Update
UpdateOperations.Description: Creates or updates a Move Resource in the move collection.

DeleteOperations.Name: Delete
DeleteOperations.Description: Deletes a Move Resource from the move collection.

ListOperations.Name: GetAll
ListOperations.Description: Lists the Move Resources in the move collection.
